Package: SeuratPipe
Type: Package
Title: Packaging common Seurat analysis tasks
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Andreas C.",
           family = "Kapourani",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kapouranis.andreas@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2303-1953"))
Description: This package contains common analysis, processing and plotting 
    functions with an attempt to streamline single-cell genomics analysis 
    using the Seurat package. This content was created to streamline analysis 
    in Neil Henderson's lab and was motivated by existing analysis approaches 
    in the lab by John Wilson-Kanamori, Jordan Portman and Nick Younger.
